qsy7-comment-remover - QSY7 Comment Remover

USAGE:
    qsy7-comment-remover [options...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Remove comments from Java files using QSY7 comment remover tool.
    Processes all files in current directory recursively.

OPTIONS:
    [options...]
        Options passed to QSY7 comment remover

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-java-qsy7-comment-remover-options OPTIONS
        Default options for QSY7 comment remover

    -qsy7-comment-remover-jar PATH
        Path to QSY7 comment remover JAR file

NOTE:
    This utility does not take filenames as arguments - it processes
    the entire current directory.

EXAMPLES:
    qsy7-comment-remover
    qsy7-comment-remover --verbose
